Menu Manipulator 3.0.1, 2021-10-24
---------------------------------
* replace {{ item.icon }} by {{ item['#icon'] }}
* filterByCurrentLanguage replaced by filterTreeByCurrentLanguage and filterItemsByCurrentLanguage
* add option to disable default filter by referenced entity
* add class on menu items with icons: "menu-item-with-icon" and"menu-item-with-icon--$icon";
* always expose Menu title and Menu description to Twig.
* simplify and improve settings form

